{"tid":136919,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎棟國：警隊大會出席者涉猶太人言論不代表警方立場","createTime":"2017-02-27T12:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T14:27:00.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58dc43d86ed4e41305ba7230989724c8eda05c8e","tid":136919,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:17:30.000Z","msg":"早前在多個警隊組織舉行的大會，有出席者發言，形容警員如同二戰時被迫害的猶太人。以色列及德國的駐港總領事館先後發聲明，指有關言論不恰當。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長黎棟國回應說，警方和相關協會已發聲明，並與領事館接觸。<br />\n<br />\n他說，言論不代表警方的立場，警方亦不認同有關言論，對此感到遺憾和難過。<br />\n<br />\n被問到警隊士氣是否低落，黎棟國說，相信每位警員都認同自己的使命，又稱對警隊有絕對信心，相信警員執行職務時，一定會公正和依法處理。"},{"pid":"1237f353dd67ed53944fda15842cce5c81fe8da2","tid":136919,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:18:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1316097-20170227.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1316097-20170227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=83ae2c86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1316097-20170227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c7f8960d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1316097-20170227.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"06eb48551e07fb230f23969845f9531a474d9266","tid":136919,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d225214a4f804946ae57b069df5bc4acd649a7","tid":136919,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffcd994524dd2b4fa26ef285aadff2e62d6c6797","tid":136919,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:20:25.000Z","msg":"講埋涉事警員點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2689ac9ad5bf888b41e2603c12da1c58f2b88d0","tid":136919,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"警方&quot;開會&quot;，但唔代表警方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我強姦女人果陣，其實我係代表緊七宗罪入面既色慾"},{"pid":"5b64a8045d7d2da91b0c2d6234e64d7220e1946b","tid":136919,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"被逼害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ec5c580943452018a40e74fd4963f9ea45511d","tid":136919,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:23:02.000Z","msg":"怪唔之得唔交不反對通知書啦<br />\n<br />\n但講完之後 成班人嗌對 bbbb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有代表性過你官方發言"},{"pid":"cacd084f3302de56e896a7ced7376d2c9efde00b","tid":136919,"uid":6647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:23:45.000Z","msg":"即刻割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8f5bb7caaa736dbbf81b04df22b299cb4fa7e0","tid":136919,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:30:43.000Z","msg":"警察協會日前發動3.3萬人「集會」，撐圍毆示威者入獄的7警，警方雖對外宣稱會上的討論屬「專業及業務性質」，但有警員上台發言時高呼「X你老母」，更自比二戰中被納粹德軍迫害的猶太人，獲全場和應，惹來以色列和德國領事館不滿。保安局局長黎棟國指，警方已發聲明，表明不認同有關言論，亦已向2個領事館解釋，有關言論不代表警方立場；員佐級協會也發聲明表示非常遺憾及難過，「我希望呢件事情得到好嘅解決」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然當晚大會在旺角警會的球場舉行，並以大聲公讓會員上台發言，傳媒在球場外，可清晰拍下發言人的講話和樣貌，惟黎棟國強調，該大會「不對外公開」，是私人性質的會員大會。雖然有警察上台時爆粗，高呼「X你老母」，更獲全場和應，但黎棟國指，會上的討論「屬於專業及業務性質議題」，坊間雖有指集會受《公安條例》涵蓋，但他指「唔係咁樣嘅事」。"},{"pid":"1dd9fc8713715ee66068bbbdd1d985dacb5ae109","tid":136919,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:31:14.000Z","msg":"被問到當晚的警察大會，有否違反警隊政治中立之嫌，黎僅稱「香港警察係一支專業嘅紀律部隊，深信每位加入警隊同事，佢哋都係認同警隊使命、工作，無論環境唔同，無論順境逆境，我哋專業嘅同事一定會、我亦對佢哋有絕對信心，喺佢哋執行職務嘅時候，一定係公正，依照法律處理。」<br />\n<br />\n他又強調，「大家可以睇到當值警務人員，依家都喺街上巡邏，執行各種職責，如果有市民打999要求警方協助，佢哋都係會喺第一時間到達現場，處理佢哋職責上需要做嘅工作，我亦深信全港市民大家會一齊支持香港警隊，維持香港治安。」<br />\n<br />\n他稱政府目前未有計劃設「辱警罪」，但會保持開放態度，聆聽意見（keep an open mind, and mind does not close）。被問到會否為七警案，向公眾道歉，黎棟國則稱案件仍上訴中，不便評論。<br />\n<br />\n當記者問及當晚的撐七察大會，多達3萬人參與，會上還高叫「爭公義、還法治」口號，會否代表警方公然挑戰司法制度時，黎回應「我絕對無依個感覺」，隨即離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170227&amp;guid=56362052&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170227%26guid%3D56362052%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=17db64ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170227%26guid%3D56362052%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=d69fc191\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170227&amp;guid=56362052&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"898cb303ecc42c6b1d12a072f49b499a41f0231e","tid":136919,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"真係當以色列同德國出完聲明就唔駛理？<br />\n<br />\n國家級層面同你交涉，你用警隊同個警察割席嚟回答？"},{"pid":"3a1e6739f0f8bb1b9d762a324f03408ae540bfbb","tid":136919,"uid":2649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:05:26.000Z","msg":"一個都走唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0c0fcd3d219696900669737ccfd31e8b472856","tid":136919,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:06:31.000Z","msg":"日頭係警察<br />\n夜晚係猶大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a07dd087d8fab297830ccf293c2fb75c88a8f1","tid":136919,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:13:52.000Z","msg":"盧偉聰一陣就會走出嚟話黎棟國言論不代表警方立場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a013d556daf9961f0943bcbe5ff08018233041f2","tid":136919,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af19fb4d657a925474f8cf2cb9dc1d234c4e42d3","tid":136919,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:27:00.000Z","msg":"警察講既野不代表警察立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}